cdata.name: BQCoin
cdata.desc: BBQCoin often abbreviated to BBQ or BQC, is a scrypt based blockchain fork of the original bitcoin source code, very similar to litecoin and launched only a short while after Litecoin. BBQcoin provides faster transaction confirmations and uses memory-hard, scrypt-based mining proof-of-work algorithm to target the regular computers and GPUs most people already have. The BBQcoin network is scheduled to produce 88 million currency units.
